videos.headline: UConn's Dorka Juhasz finishes off a tough and-1
videos.description: Dorka Juhasz drops in an and-1 to extend the Huskies' early lead. (edited)

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn’s Dorka Juhasz finishes off a tough and-1) 2021/12/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paige Bueckers splashing 3s less than a week after surgery
videos.description: Injured UConn star Paige Bueckers drains some 3-pointers on one leg before the Huskies' game against No. 6 Louisville.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Paige Bueckers splashing threes less than a week after surgery) 2021/12/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Evina Westbrook blocks a shot, drops a dime on the other end
videos.description: UConn's Evina Westbrook blocks a shot, keeps the ball in bounds and drops a dime on the other side for the Huskies.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Evina Westbrook blocks a shot, drops a dime on the other end) 2021/12/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hailey Van Lith knocks down a huge 3-pointer for the Cardinals
videos.description: Louisville's Hailey Van Lith nails the catch-and-shoot 3-pointer to extend her team's lead in the fourth quarter.
